Package org.opensaml.saml.saml2.metadata Description

Concrete definitions of the objects described in saml-metadata-2.0-os work. Information on using this library can be found in the User's Manual and information on extending its functionality can be found in the Developer's Manual. see OpenSAML Wiki.
